Operational scripting (bash/python) and automation

Not recommended to own

Final architecture decisions

Security/compliance sign-off

Production deploy / direct cluster admin operations

2.2 Delphin AI (Orchestrator / Workflow Agent Platform)

What it does

Assigns tasks to AI agents (coding, QA, docs)

Integrates with Jira/Git/CI (typical pattern)

Enforces guardrails (e.g., â€œno prod accessâ€, â€œno secretsâ€)

Maintains audit trail and change history

Standardizes prompts and outputs

Best fit tasks in EAP

Auto-triage tickets (categorize: infra / app / cert / OpenShift / CM)

Enforce consistent engineering workflow

Coordinate: Devin (coding) + QA agent (tests) + Doc agent (Confluence updates)

Provide weekly metrics and outcomes for leadership

